        </div>
        <div>
          <img loading="lazy" src="/images/thor2/thor2-buy-feature.webp" alt="雷神之錘2 買免遊介面" width="600" height="338" style="width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:10px;border:2px solid var(--guava-pink)">
          <p style="text-align:center;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0.3rem 0 0">▲ 雷神2 買免遊 — 三段選擇 x100/x500/x4000</p>
